reviewText: I love this family!  I have been intrigued by their journey.  They are beautiful, witty, and entrepreneurial.

Loved watching every episode! Not a fan of the Braxtons mum & this business of trying to get hooked up. She needs a new storyline. The sisters on the other hand were extremely entertaining . Can't wait to watch volume 2.
Love Toni Braxton and her sisters funny entertaining and interesting especially Tamar point blank period you go girl cray silly.

Ok first I must say I love the Braxton Sisters. This TV Series is wonderful. Its fun, exciting and emotional. I would definitely recommend Braxton Family Values to everyone. You should start with the first season then work your way to the 3rd.

What a shame, this is a great show, but the advertised photo makes you think your getting Season Three, but your only getting a few episodes of Season Three.  That's a pretty deceitful tactic, especially when most other reality shows give you all the DVD's for a given season.
Great show. Very exciting I hope you release more shows on dvd to be purchased. I only have a few because you only have a few on your website to be purchased but i want them all.
i couldn't enjoy the show. because it would pause and then stop. and i was so excited too watch it.
The drama is just ridiculous but I love it.
favorite reality show on dvd...love it

The Braxtons help you see that no matter what walk of life we come from it is all much the same. Every walk has good times and bad times. Hard times and easy times. We all have laughter and tears. So no matter weather we live the lime light life or the quiet country life we ALL deal with the same issues one way or another. Jenny
